sequenceDiagram
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService
    participant Knative as Knative Eventing
    participant CloudEvt as CloudEventConsumer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MMesh as ModelMesh<br/>Payload Processor
    participant Consumer as ConsumerEndpoint<br/>/consumer/kserve/v2
    participant Reconciler as PayloadReconciler<br/>(KServe or ModelMesh)
    participant Storage as DataSource<br/>(PVC / Hibernate / MinIO)
    participant Scheduler as PrometheusScheduler<br/>(@Scheduled 5s)
    participant Metrics as Metric Calculator<br/>(SPD/DIR/KS/MMD)
    participant Micrometer as Micrometer Registry<br/>/q/metrics
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus Server
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Explainer as Explainer Endpoint<br/>/explainers/local/*
    participant Model as KServe Model Server<br/>gRPC v2
    participant DB as MariaDB/MySQL<br/>3306/TCP JDBC

    Note over KServe,Storage: Flow 1: Inference Data Ingestion via CloudEvents (KServe)
    KServe->>Knative: CloudEvent (org.kubeflow.serving.inference.request/response)<br/>GZIP-compressed
    Knative->>CloudEvt: HTTP POST CloudEvent<br/>8080/TCP, No TLS
    CloudEvt->>Reconciler: KServeInferencePayloadReconciler<br/>In-process Java call
    Reconciler->>Storage: Persist matched input/output pair<br/>Java method / JDBC 3306/TCP
    Storage->>DB: INSERT (if Hibernate backend)<br/>MySQL wire protocol, DB credentials

    Note over MMesh,Storage: Flow 2: Inference Data Ingestion via REST (ModelMesh)
    MMesh->>Consumer: HTTP POST JSON<br/>8080/TCP, No TLS, No Auth
    Consumer->>Reconciler: ModelMeshInferencePayloadReconciler<br/>In-process Java call
    Reconciler->>Storage: Persist inference payload<br/>Java method / JDBC 3306/TCP

    Note over Scheduler,Prometheus: Flow 3: Scheduled Fairness/Drift Metrics to Prometheus
    loop Every 5 seconds (configurable)
        Scheduler->>Storage: Load inference data (batched, max 50000)<br/>In-process / JDBC
        Storage-->>Scheduler: Inference records
        Scheduler->>Metrics: Compute SPD, DIR, KS-test, Fourier MMD, Meanshift<br/>In-process Java call
        Metrics-->>Scheduler: Computed metric values
        Scheduler->>Micrometer: Publish trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir gauges<br/>Micrometer API
    end
    Prometheus->>Micrometer: HTTP GET /q/metrics<br/>8080/TCP, Bearer Token (SA token)
    Micrometer-->>Prometheus: Prometheus text format metrics

    Note over User,Model: Flow 4: On-Demand Explainability Request (disabled in RHOAI)
    User->>Explainer: HTTP POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>8080/TCP, No TLS, No Auth
    Explainer->>Storage: Load background data<br/>In-process / JDBC
    Storage-->>Explainer: Background dataset
    Explainer->>Model: gRPC ModelInfer (KServe v2)<br/>model-port/TCP, plaintext, No Auth
    Model-->>Explainer: Prediction results
    Explainer-->>User: HTTP JSON response<br/>Explanation (saliency map)
